data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Charming Freshly Painted Brick Ranch Home w/ NO HOA in sought after Ivy Falls Plantation with double garage. SOLAR PANEL SYSTEM INSTALLED & POWER BILL AS LOW AS $25.00 MONTHLY! NEW ROOF INSTALLED IN 2020!  The open foyer welcomes guests with formal dining area and built-in shelves surround the gas fireplace in the great room. Step inside to discover an open split floor plan that welcomes you with hardwood floors that extend throughout the formal dining room, great room, sunroom/study, and kitchen. A walk-in laundry room conveniently located off the open kitchen adds functionality to your daily routine. With its eat-in breakfast area and prep island, this kitchen is both stylish and practical. A delightful screened-in porch with a patio-sized fenced backyard is thoughtfully designed for easy upkeep, allowing you more time to unwind and savor life's simple pleasures. Convenient to schools, Ft. Gordon, Shopping, Restaurants, I-520 & I-20. Come see, won't last long!
